    "body": "<!--üîÖüîÖüîÖüîÖüîÖüîÖüîÖüîÖüîÖüîÖüîÖüîÖüîÖüîÖüîÖüîÖüîÖüîÖüîÖüîÖüîÖüîÖüîÖüîÖüîÖüîÖüîÖüîÖüîÖüîÖüîÖ\r\n\r\nOh hi there! üòÑ\r\n\r\nTo expedite issue processing please search open and closed issues before submitting a new one.\r\nExisting issues often contain information about workarounds, resolution, or progress updates.\r\n\r\nüîÖüîÖüîÖüîÖüîÖüîÖüîÖüîÖüîÖüîÖüîÖüîÖüîÖüîÖüîÖüîÖüîÖüîÖüîÖüîÖüîÖüîÖüîÖüîÖüîÖüîÖüîÖüîÖüîÖüîÖüîÖüîÖüîÖ-->\r\n\r\n\r\n# üêû bug report\r\n\r\n### Affected Package\r\n\r\nThe issue is caused by package @angular/common or @ngtools/webpack\r\n\r\n### Description\r\n\r\nI have 2 routes, one for the app module and one for the tabs module. \r\n#### App routes\r\n```\r\nconst routes: Routes = [\r\n  { path: '', redirectTo: 'home', pathMatch: 'full' },\r\n  {\r\n    path: 'home',\r\n    loadChildren: './pages/home/home.module#HomePageModule'\r\n  },\r\n  { path: 'page/:pageName', loadChildren: './pages/page/page.module#PagePageModule' },\r\n\r\n  {\r\n    path: '',\r\n    loadChildren: './tabs/tabs.module#TabsPageModule'\r\n  }\r\n]\r\n```\r\n\r\n#### App routes\r\n```\r\nconst routes: Routes = [\r\n  {\r\n    path: 'tabs',\r\n    component: TabsPage,\r\n    children: [\r\n      {\r\n        path: '',\r\n        redirectTo: '/tabs/tabproduct',\r\n        pathMatch: 'full'\r\n      },\r\n      {\r\n        path: 'tabproduct',\r\n        children: [\r\n          {\r\n            path: '',\r\n            loadChildren: '../pages/tabproduct/tabproduct.module#TabproductPageModule'\r\n          }\r\n        ]\r\n      },\r\n      {\r\n        path: 'tabstory',\r\n        children: [\r\n          {\r\n            path: '',\r\n            loadChildren: '../pages/tabstory/tabstory.module#TabstoryPageModule'\r\n          }\r\n        ]\r\n      },\r\n      {\r\n        path: 'tab/:id',\r\n        children: [\r\n          {\r\n            path: '',\r\n            loadChildren: '../pages/tab/tab.module#TabPageModule'\r\n          }\r\n        ]\r\n      }\r\n    ]\r\n  },\r\n  {\r\n    path: '',\r\n    redirectTo: '/tabs/tabproduct',\r\n    pathMatch: 'full'\r\n  }\r\n]\r\n```\r\n\r\nOn server side, I have a folder per version (v0.0, v0.1 ... v1.3 ...). I set up a default behavior in order to redirect on a version.\r\nEx: https://my.app.com/home -> returns the default version in the folder v1.3 for instance\r\n\r\nSo in my index.html, I have deleted the `<base href=\"/\" />` tag and put a script instead :  \r\n```\r\n<script type='text/javascript'>\r\n    let firstPathname = window.location.pathname.split('/')[1]\r\n    console.log(firstPathname)\r\n\r\n    let regexVersioningTag = new RegExp(\"^v\");\r\n    let result = regexVersioningTag.test(firstPathname);\r\n    // if there is a version number\r\n    if(result){ window['_app_base_href'] = '/' + firstPathname; }\r\n</script>\r\n```\r\nSo if there is an app version in the URL, the script stores it in a global variable.\r\n\r\nIn the app.module, I set the APP_BASE_HREF to the global variable or, by default, to '/' : \r\n```\r\n@NgModule({\r\n  declarations: [AppComponent],\r\n  entryComponents: [],\r\n  imports: [\r\n    IonicModule.forRoot(),\r\n    IonicStorageModule.forRoot(),\r\n    AppRoutingModule,\r\n  ],\r\n  providers: [\r\n    StatusBar,\r\n    SplashScreen,\r\n    { provide: RouteReuseStrategy, useClass: IonicRouteStrategy },\r\n    { provide: APP_BASE_HREF, useValue: window['_app_base_href'] || '/' }\r\n  ],\r\n  bootstrap: [AppComponent],\r\n  schemas: [NO_ERRORS_SCHEMA]\r\n})\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\n## üî¨ Issue\r\n\r\nWhen I access to home page, it works like a charm ! (ie: https://my.app.com/home)\r\n\r\nWhen I access to tabproduct page (ie: https://my.app.com/tabs.tabproduct), the browser produces errors because it's trying to get /tabs/{scripts.js} (but the page loads). \r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/38292202/58268988-d1c5c680-7d86-11e9-8219-6dc67e79e909.png)\r\n\r\nHowever, the tags scripts in the index.html are good !\r\n  \r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/38292202/58268975-ca9eb880-7d86-11e9-8617-8d7b03fbabce.png)\r\n\r\n\r\n## üåç  Your Environment\r\n\r\n**Angular Version:**\r\n@angular-devkit/build-webpack     0.13.8\r\n@angular-devkit/core              7.3.5\r\n@angular-devkit/schematics        7.3.5\r\n@angular/cli                      7.3.5\r\n@angular/compiler                 7.2.2\r\n@angular/compiler-cli             7.2.8\r\n@ngtools/webpack                  7.3.8\r\nwebpack                           4.29.0\r\n\r\n"
