    "body": "Updates the size-tracking golden for the `core_all` test of the\r\n`@angular/core` package.\r\n\r\nEven though the size comparison test is not enabled right now,\r\nwe should update the size-tracking golden since the `rules_nodejs`\r\ncommit that fixes the source-maps for external packages has been\r\nreleased. See: https://github.com/bazelbuild/rules_nodejs/commit/f5314b43d7e1bb25ad6085e596b05882e4941499\r\n\r\nThis ensures that future manual golden comparisons are less verbose\r\nand it's easier to observe large size changes."
